name: alkene,NADH:oxygen oxidoreductase
definition: Propylene + NADH + H+ + Oxygen <=> (2R)-1,2-Epoxypropane + NAD+ + H2O
comment: The stereospecifity of the epoxypropane formed is 95% (R). see R05730 ((S)-formed)
